        "description": "在连续流动固定床反应器中，使用不同Ni/脱硅介孔沸石催化剂（10Ni/Hbeta, 10Ni/NH4-ZSM-5, 10Ni/USY及其脱硅变体），在375–475°C温度和15–25 bar氢气压力下，对棕榈油进行催化加氢处理，生产生物航煤（C8-C16烃类）。",
        "text_snippet": "The experiments were carried out in a continuous-flow fixed-bed reactor at different conditions; temperatures of 375–475°C and hydrogen pressures of 15–25bar... focused on the bio-jet fuel production from hydroprocessing of palm oil over different types of Ni/desilicated mesoporous zeolites",
